OL,5, It's been the object of much           
OL,6, speculation for weeks: who would lead  
OL,7, Silvio Berlusconi's empire after his   
OL,8, death?                                 
OL,10,FNow his will has been made public, it  
OL,11,Fis clear he has handed a majority stake
OL,12,Fin the family's holding company        
OL,13,FFininvest to his two eldest children,  
OL,14,FMarina and Pier Silvio.                
OL,16,FThey will jointly own 53% of the family
OL,17,Ffirm.                                  
OL,20,FBut he never publicly indicated who    
OL,21,Fshould lead his business empire.       
